X.
Mr. Vincent Maloney, Organizer,
American Federation of Labor,
241 E. 10th St., Oswego, New York.

Dear Sir and Brother:

Your favor of the fourth instant received and contents noted. I am this day writing to the International Association of Machinists and the United Brotherhood of Boiler Makers requesting that their respective local unions in Oswego be urged to affiliate with the Central Labor Union in accordance with the Constitution.

With best wishes, I am,
fraternally yours,
Samuel Gompers
President, American Federation of Labor,
(Per R. L. G.)
